<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 0824 _ At first glance, a compact truck with
extended cab, third door and four-wheel drive might seem like a
niche vehicle targeting buyers who really go off-roading. But spend
some time and miles with Chevrolet's S-10 with those features, and
it all makes a lot of sense. (DeVault, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) Art includes 3-column color photo of 1999
Chevrolet S-10 and a 18-pica color photo of the truck's interior.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: AT A GLANCE _ Fact box previewing the 1999 Chevrolet S-10
</P>
<P>
   WITH: THE MECHANIC _ I am deeply concerned about the future of
the auto repair industry as it relates to the seemingly endless
complexity of features being engineered into new vehicles. (Carter,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). Includes 1-column color photograph
of columnist.
