<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-24 12:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7645 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k BC-LYNCH-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      08-24 0659
