pretty good right now,'' Alexander admitted, ``and I was furious
when I went in there.''
 &HT;    It turned out that the night before, he had a conversation with
a girl that took a decidedly unsatisfying turn at the end.
 &HT;    I'm not so worried about kids like Alexander _ he clearly has
demonstrated both the discipline to remake his appearance and the
psychological distance not to take it, or himself, too seriously.
 &HT;    But there will be many other boys out there who cannot hope to
