concerned about you.''
 &HT;    ``Nothing to be concerned about,'' J. replied.
 &HT;    ``Do you want to go to the office?'' she asked.
 &HT;    ``Hell, no,'' he said. Then she sent him there.
 &HT;    Ordinarily, J. would have been sent home for cursing. He knew
the drill. This time, however, he would wait for the Peterborough
