</P>
<P>
   T H E M E N U
</P>
<P>
   By the way, food will be served on these tables. Here's what
Tony Conway's Legendary Events has cooked up for a ``Designer
Summer Supper'':
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Grilled yellow and red tomato gazpacho served in a martini
glass with fresh basil and cracked peppered lavash
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Summer lettuces with vine-ripened Roma tomatoes, English
cucumbers, buffalo mozzarella, arugula and a pest vinaigrette
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Marinated grilled chicken breast with champagne sauce
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  A chocolate leopard-skin box filled with summer sweet
surprises
</P>
<P>
   _ Danny C. Flanders
</P>
