<P>
   ELWAY-ONLINE _ ATLANTA _ Pro football great John Elway partners
with Atlanta firm to develop new Web site focusing on sports and
fitness for men 35 and older. The Atlanta firm had originally
suggested Elway be a spokesman for an online brokerage firm they
were developing, but Elway decided to take the venture in a
different direction. Site is expected to launch during the Super
Bowl in Atlanta in January. (Katz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   DELL _ AUSTIN, Texas _ More than 1,400 customers and computer
industry big wigs start arriving in Austin today for Dell's
Directconnect gathering. We chat up those who are arriving. Why are
they here? What are they hoping to hear from the likes of Michael
Dell, Bill Gates, Craig Barrett? And do they have confidence in
those three to meet demands in the growing Internet economy?
(Mahoney, Austin American-Statesman)
