<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COX NEWS SERVICE SPORTS BUDGET
 &HT;    c. 1999 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   These sports stories for release Wednesday, August 25, 1999, are
moving today to clients of the New York Times News Service.
