<P>
   XMAS-EARLY (Los Angeles) _ Forget what the calendar says; it's
beginning to look a lot like Christmas. True, every year people
complain that Christmas _ or, more accurately, Christmas displays
at local stores _ comes earlier each year. But really, this year it
has come early then it ever has before, hasn't it? By Dave McNary.
