the last time he was in the United States, Winfrey turned down his
offer to be on the show.
</P>
<P>
   A representative for Harpo (Winfrey's production company) said
it's true that the Dalai Lama and Winfrey had ``scheduling
conflicts'' for this visit, but she could not confirm any
negotiations about prior visits.
</P>
