Giants free safety Percy Ellsworth during a team practice on
Tuesday. The Giants have done little to distort the importance of
their preseason meeting this weekend with the Jets. With starting
jobs on the line and key players returning from injury, mythical
territorial struggles hardly raise the stakes in the preseason.
(David Jennings/New York Times Photo)
</P>
