<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-24 23:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8401 &Cx1f; tic-z
u v BC-ADD-BUDGET-AZR     08-24 0166
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ADD-BUDGET-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
